{"tid":1172020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海關截美國寄港毒郵包 檢57萬元大麻花拘19歲仔","createTime":"2019-05-26T06:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T11:43:52.000Z","uid":54733,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"046689e9f96b0e091fb453849fdea8f45c0f8ce6","tid":1172020,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PSdE_gFwXUJEqXSteCZnzg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/a657aeea5e9980792fa27627f04de963\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPSdE_gFwXUJEqXSteCZnzg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fa657aeea5e9980792fa27627f04de963&h=01877dbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LrD_k_dNu5eBKh8NJNSaoA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/b1055966054fd698e9d1c1d4dcdad70c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLrD_k_dNu5eBKh8NJNSaoA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fb1055966054fd698e9d1c1d4dcdad70c&h=fa628931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=71097ce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】海關又破獲「毒郵包」。本周一(20日)，海關人員在香港國際機場貨運站，截查一個由美國寄抵港郵包，該紙箱郵包呎半乘呎半，報稱為衣物，關員透過X光機檢查，懷疑內藏可疑物品，遂拆開調查，發現藏有約3公斤懷疑大麻花，分別以6個密封膠袋盛載，並用衣物遮蓋掩飾，該批毒品總值約57萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其後，海關毒品調查科機場調查課接手追查，根據郵包的收件人及地址等資料，昨日(22日)掩至柴灣區埋伏，一名青年收取郵包時，隨即上前將他拘捕。昨日疑犯已獲准保釋候查，海關正追查毒品來源及及分銷渠道。海關表示，會與香港郵政及物流業界保持緊密聯繫，加強堵截利用郵遞或速遞渠道偷運毒品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海關續指，根據《危險藥物條例》，販運危險藥物屬嚴重罪行，一經定罪，最高可被判罰款五百萬元及終身監禁。海關同時提醒公眾人士，大麻及四氫大麻酚屬《條例》定明的危險藥物。除非符合《條例》的相關要求，否則進口含有大麻或四氫大麻酚的產品（包括食品或飲料）一律被禁止。市民須留意有關產品的包裝標示，以免誤墮法網。"},{"pid":"6a4fa955e6a86d1d1e7c1b06fb171f2afcf2f1a0","tid":1172020,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:49:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/海關截美國寄港毒郵包-檢57萬元大麻花拘19歲仔-102341660.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E6%88%AA%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AF%84%E6%B8%AF%E6%AF%92%E9%83%B5%E5%8C%85-%E6%AA%A257%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB%E8%8A%B1%E6%8B%9819%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%94-102341660.html&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=572b31d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/海關截美國寄港毒郵包-檢57萬元大麻花拘19歲仔-102341660.html</a>"},{"pid":"5fa9ac3dd7b46940aa80bb6b941bb6acce75b871","tid":1172020,"uid":7854,"like":52,"dislike":8,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"大麻吸毒chill撚:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/polymerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/%E7%8A%AF%E5%92%97%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%88%E9%BB%9E%E5%96%8E-%EF%BC%9F.jpg?fit=698%2C520\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fpolymerhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2F%25E7%258A%25AF%25E5%2592%2597%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%258F%2588%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2596%258E-%25EF%25BC%259F.jpg%3Ffit%3D698%252C520&h=a05dff97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b3f5b319740f6d2c9912302fd2b2f88d7c71ac6","tid":1172020,"uid":113626,"like":8,"dislike":33,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:53:23.000Z","msg":"大麻明明傷害仲低過食煙都要禁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c133c6e8941e2525afd523798296c9ebe1f8ea","tid":1172020,"uid":23400,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:54:00.000Z","msg":"創意台班盲毛上水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmo