律被禁止。市民須留意有關產品的包裝標示，以免誤墮法網。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:56:27.000Z","msg":"第二幅圖，呀Sir 你眼好紅喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係係大倉同老孭驗貨吓嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">JK</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:57:47.000Z","msg":"肯定廿個鐘無訓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c529f23bab049211bcb2229a9acff8cc27f385","tid":1172020,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fa83f77652c076704f405cfb5a62f05fb4db40","tid":1172020,"uid":6329,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"其實唔明點解收都犯法<br />\n如果無啦啦有人寄毒品俾我，我又唔知係毒品，走去收咪仆街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092df94ffd78179034fc9d3c4695db55edc5e8fd","tid":1172020,"uid":25367,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"邊位道友巴打？唔係好鍾意隊草㗎咩？上到庭同法官講大麻好有藥用價值喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd023a517e0704abadbede09ff5976142eb6f31","tid":1172020,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T07:23:01.000Z","msg":"又小一個人同我競爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee30857ba21ec6dc9c84f1a77408defe9dc78343","tid":1172020,"uid":175661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51e5b3f271fc9d67343c9bc9a159a16ab5cb8c05","tid":1172020,"uid":241545,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"f973fc3d4416a88320ac3990f0f67f6def724e32","tid":1172020,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:54:16.000Z","msg":"拉收件人唔係拉寄件人?"},"citedBy":3,"rep